# Overview

This rule enforces the Sweet Pastel Design Manual and structural principles for the Wan-Lebel website.  
All UI, layout, typography, interaction, and content structure must strictly follow these constraints.

The goal is to create a calm, trustworthy, low-stimulation experience that reduces anxiety while prioritizing reservation conversion.

---

# Brand Philosophy

Core concept:
"第二のおうちのような、やさしく包む空間"

Design must:
- Reduce anxiety
- Avoid visual noise
- Maintain soft atmosphere
- Avoid aggressive marketing tone
- Prioritize reservation clarity

Cuteness is a result, not the objective.

---

# Business Model Constraints

- Reservation is the highest priority action.
- No prepayment system is used.
- Payment is made at the salon after service.
- Online reservation is the main booking method.
- LINE is for consultation only, not primary booking.

Reservation CTA must always be visually dominant.

---

# Color System (Strict)

Main: #F5E1E6  
Base: #FFFBFB  
Text: #6B5E62  
Accent: #C2E0EB  

Prohibited:
- #000000
- Pure black text
- Vivid colors
- Red emphasis
- Multi-color gradients

Color balance:
Base ~45%
Main ~35%
Text ~15%
Accent ~5-10%

Only ONE primary accent element per section.

---

# Typography

Primary: "Zen Maru Gothic"
Fallback: "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif

Headings: font-weight 700
Body: font-weight 400

Line-height: 1.8

Do not overuse bold text.
Do not use heavy font contrasts.

---

# Layout System

Max width: 1100px
Centered layout

Section spacing:
- Desktop: minimum 80px vertical
- Mobile: minimum 48px vertical

Card padding: minimum 24px

One message per section.
Avoid dense content.
Avoid large text blocks.

Whitespace equals psychological safety.

---

# UI Components

Primary CTA Button:
- Background: #C2E0EB
- Text: #6B5E62
- Border-radius: 9999px
- Subtle shadow
- Hover: slight elevation only

Cards:
- Background: white
- Border-radius: 16px
- Soft shadow
- No heavy borders

Icons:
- Line-based preferred
- Minimal fill
- Rounded style

---

# Navigation Rules

Desktop:
- Fixed header allowed
- Must include link to /menu, /access, /faq
- Reservation button visible

Mobile:
- Fixed bottom navigation required
- Exactly 3 items only:
  1. Reservation (primary, accent)
  2. Menu
  3. LINE consultation

Do NOT add more than 3 items.
Reservation must be visually dominant.

---

# Structural Rules

Homepage must include:

1. Hero
2. Trust section (3 cards)
3. Service summary
4. Pricing overview (linked to /menu)
5. Instagram reference
6. Access (small embedded map)
7. FAQ (3 items)
8. Final CTA

Homepage should feel complete,
but deeper information must link to:

- /menu
- /access
- /faq
- /policy

SEO pages must exist separately.

---

# SEO and Content Tone

Tone:
- Polite Japanese
- Calm
- No hype
- No pressure language

Forbidden wording:
- 最安値
- 圧倒的
- 今すぐ
- 絶対

Include naturally:
- 山口市
- 犬専門
- トリミング
- サロン
- ペットホテル

Do not keyword stuff.
Write for humans first.

